text: Aleksandr Belanovsky (born 3 May 1972) is a Belarusian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Belarus Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Minsk
